rce%3Dyoutube&v=mojZpktAiYQ) … ...more\\n\\n...more\\n\\n## Comments 182 ## In this video\\n\\nChapters\\n\\nTranscript ## Description\\n\\nA Complete Guide To Vercel’s AI SDK // The ESSENTIAL Tool For Shipping AI Apps\\n\\n3\\\\.9K Likes 94,222 Views 2025 Jan 21 The Tutorial: [https://www.aihero.dev/vercel-ai-sdk-...](https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDVpRkxHTGJHeUZZaFIwVURGWmczOWVMVXpFQXxBQ3Jtc0trWUNvVEFxQ2VsSk1TSHdGbEFfZG10UjJBSlViQVR6TVRNTjZocUktMXhBWEFqMDdieU42SWh1aTlFeW9sUGJuVHVPWFMwbHBuSk82REtKOFBrVDNXeWVLWmJoSVc0Y0xlMngxeTBlRTVhN0VWSHg4NA&q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aihero.dev%2Fvercel-ai-sdk-tutorial%3Futm_source%3Dyoutube&v=mojZpktAiYQ) Join The Newsletter: [https://www.aihero.\\ndev/newsletter?utm...](https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqblphU1Q4Mzc3MnYzTTBySlB6LXk3UEU3eV9LZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttRkJFZFlrU1lmSXVvYkMyZGhPWGdHQ19PMTNFOUNjcC13QjBybmllaWVrRVJ3SU4tN0dEaXkxTk90UjAtODRpZ25WZlBiZlpHMW5pNnQ4aF9rRXZITVZaLWVtTTBRU0Q3bGQ4RUVpTWRzQ1Jzc0xQTQ&q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aihero.dev%2Fnewsletter%3Futm_source%3Dyoutube&v=mojZpktAiYQ) 00:00 Intro 01:20 What Is The AI SDK? 03:23 generateText 04:58 streamText 06:02 System Prompts 06:52 Hot-Swapping Models 07:57 Preserving Chat History 12:38 Running Local Models 13:49 Structured Outputs 16:21 Streaming Structured Outputs 18:07 Building A Classifier 19:36 Describing Images 23:10 Data Extraction From PDF's 26:04 Embeddings & Vector Databases 30:08 Tool Calling 33:46 Your First Agent 37:44 Outro Follow Matt on Twitter [/ mattpocockuk](https://www.youtube.com/redirect?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"deff4dc97f18b237\\\">>>\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"02e63f573fdedea9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVercel AI SDK Tutorial\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"02e63f573fdedea9\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.aihero.dev/vercel-ai-sdk-tutorial\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2efb00c0ec2ca83c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n---\\ntitle: \\\"Vercel AI SDK Tutorial\\\"\\nslug: \\\"vercel-ai-sdk-tutorial\\\"\\ntype: \\\"list\\\"\\ndescription: \\\"Build any LLM app in TypeScript with Vercel's AI SDK. Learn streaming, structured outputs, tool calls and agents.\\\"\\ntags:\\n  - Vercel AI SDK\\n---\\n\\nI've been building a lot of stuff with TypeScript and AI recently. I've been building agents, workflows, custom scripts and CLIs to help me work faster and smarter.\\n\\nAnd Vercel's AI SDK has been an awesome tool in my toolkit.\\n\\nIt's a library that solves a lot of the pain points when working with LLMs.\\n\\nAnd in this tutorial, I'm going to give you a full guide on how to get to grips with it.\\n\\n<Testimonial authorName=\\\"Addy Osmani — Engineering leader @ Google Chrome\\\" authorAvatar=\\\"http://res.cloudinary.com/total-typescript/image/upload/v1737461573/posts/list-40v10/sopfsrvcgstoclcusbui.jpg\\\">\\nThis is really good! Learned a few things I didn't know.\\n</Testimonial>\\n\\nWe're going to cover:\\n\\n<ul data-checklist=\\\"\\\">\\n<li>Hot-swapping models</li>\\n<li>Streaming</li>\\n<li>Structured outputs</li>\\n<li>Handling images and files</li>\\n<li>Tool calling</li>\\n<li>Building agents</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\nYou can use the AI SDK Core anywhere JavaScript runs. And that's why I'm so excited about it. It's so versatile, so powerful and it's just the right level of abstraction for almost any task.\\n\\nHead to [AI Hero's GitHub Repo](https://github.com/ai-hero-dev/ai-hero/) for all the code, and to run the examples.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2efb00c0ec2ca83c\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.aihero.dev\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2efb00c0ec2ca83c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n---\\ntitle: \\\"Vercel AI SDK Tutorial\\\"\\nslug: \\\"vercel-ai-sdk-tutorial\\\"\\ntype: \\\"list\\\"\\ndescription: \\\"Build any LLM app in TypeScript with Vercel's AI SDK. Learn streaming, structured outputs, tool calls and agents.\\\"\\ntags:\\n  - Vercel AI SDK\\n---\\n\\nI've been building a lot of stuff with TypeScript and AI recently. I've been building agents, workflows, custom scripts and CLIs to help me work faster and smarter.\\n\\nAnd Vercel's AI SDK has been an awesome tool in my toolkit.\\n\\nIt's a library that solves a lot of the pain points when working with LLMs.\\n\\nAnd in this tutorial, I'm going to give you a full guide on how to get to grips with it.\\n\\n<Testimonial authorName=\\\"Addy Osmani — Engineering leader @ Google Chrome\\\" authorAvatar=\\\"http://res.cloudinary.com/total-typescript/image/upload/v1737461573/posts/list-40v10/sopfsrvcgstoclcusbui.jpg\\\">\\nThis is really good! Learned a few things I didn't know.\\n</Testimonial>\\n\\nWe're going to cover:\\n\\n<ul data-checklist=\\\"\\\">\\n<li>Hot-swapping models</li>\\n<li>Streaming</li>\\n<li>Structured outputs</li>\\n<li>Handling images and files</li>\\n<li>Tool calling</li>\\n<li>Building agents</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\nYou can use the AI SDK Core anywhere JavaScript runs. And that's why I'm so excited about it. It's so versatile, so powerful and it's just the right level of abstraction for almost any task.\\n\\nHead to [AI Hero's GitHub Repo](https://github.com/ai-hero-dev/ai-hero/) for all the code, and to run the examples.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2efb00c0ec2ca83c\\\">>>\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4fac83bfb2ef0e83\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Set Up Vercel AI SDK: A Practical Guide - Hyperion Consulting\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4fac83bfb2ef0e83\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://hyperion-consulting.io/en/insights/how-to-set-up-vercel-ai-sdk-a-practical-guide\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d94fcbbc1b89daf6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHyperion Consulting logo - AI 